item.title: CVE-2023-35991|2024-10-21T20:26:02.037Z -- logitec%20corporation -- lan-w300n%2Fdr
item.description: Hidden functionality vulnerability in LOGITEC wireless LAN routers allows an unauthenticated attacker to log in to the product's certain management console and execute arbitrary OS commands. Affected products and versions are as follows: LAN-W300N/DR all versions, LAN-WH300N/DR all versions, LAN-W300N/P all versions, LAN-WH450N/GP all versions, LAN-WH300AN/DGP all versions, LAN-WH300N/DGP all versions, and LAN-WH300ANDGPE all versions.
